videos.description: Frank Mason III gets into the lane and throws up the lob to Landen Lucas who finishes with the two-hand flush to get Kansas flying early.
videos.headline: Lucas has Kansas flying high with alley-oop finish
S. Mykhailiuk gets the steal and gets the layup to go

videos.description: 1H (1:11) KU Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Frank Mason III.
videos.headline: Kansas uses some good ball movement and hits the open 3 pointer

videos.description: Kansas has everything going against Nebraska, including Devonte' Graham getting the friendly roll from a deep 3-pointer to end the half with a 54-34 lead.
videos.headline: Kansas' Graham drains deep 3 to beat the halftime buzzer

videos.description: Frank Mason III glides through the defense and hits the tough layup while falling over to get the bucket and the foul for Kansas.
videos.headline: Mason hits the tough layup and-1 to keep Kansas rolling

videos.headline: A. Gill made Dunk. Assisted by T. Webster.
Kansas gets the steal but Josh Jackson cant finish the big dunk

videos.headline: J. Jackson made Dunk. Assisted by L. Lucas.

videos.description: Svi Mykhailiuk tries tossing the lob off the glass, but Josh Jackson is unable to finish the dunk leaving Bill Self none too pleased in the second half against Nebraska.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jackson misses dunk after Kansas gets too fancy) 2016/12/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jackson misses dunk after Kansas gets too fancy

videos.description: Devonte' Graham makes the spin move to get around a defense and then throws the bounce pass to a streaking Josh Jackson for the massive slam to put the exclamation point on a Kansas win.
videos.headline: Graham's sweet move leads to awesome Jackson dunk

videos.description: Kansas' Josh Jackson breaks down his 17-point game against Nebraska and credits chemistry for Jayhawks' 9-1 run.
videos.headline: Josh Jackson emphasizes team work in win over Nebraska
